DESCRIPTION:
    A simple script to change interface mac addresses to a set value or random value


USAGE:
    macchanger.sh [interface, macAddress]


EXAMPLE:
    macchanger.sh wlan0 ca:fe:ca:fe:ca:fe   # sets mac address for interface
    - OR - 
    macchanger.sh wlan0 ca:fe:ca:fe:ca:fe   # generates and sets randaom mac address for interface
